  "requirement_refs": ["FR-048"],
  "note": "Contract predicates under test are pure (except the path-safety symlink check). Plan/command shapes mirror contracts/verification-plan.schema.json. Path-bearing command cases are validated against the real repo root by the test. The 'example-not-a-real-secret' literal is a rejection FIXTURE, never a real value.",

  "plan_cases": [
